## ğŸ› ï¸ Lab Challenge: Create an Animated Landing Page  

ğŸ“Œ **Task:** Create a landing page with:  
âœ… **A heading that fades in**  
âœ… **A button that changes size on hover**  
âœ… **A background that slides in from the side**  

ğŸ”¹ **Example HTML**  
```html
<header class="hero">
  <h1 class="title">Welcome to My Website</h1>
  <button class="cta">Get Started</button>
</header>
```

ğŸ”¹ **Example CSS**  
```css
.hero {
  background-color: blue;
  padding: 50px;
  text-align: center;
  animation: slideIn 1s ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes slideIn {
  from { transform: translateY(-100px); opacity: 0; }
  to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

.cta {
  background-color: yellow;
  padding: 10px;
  font-size: 20px;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.cta:hover {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}
```

ğŸ¯ **Bonus:** Add a **looping animation to make elements float slightly!**  

